---
description: Diagram output rules for mobile review (Matheus)
alwaysApply: true
---

When creating or updating architecture/flow diagrams for this repo:

1. Add or update source in `docs/mermaid/*.mmd`
2. Run `./scripts/render-diagrams.sh` to produce `docs/images/*.png`
3. **Always give PNG links** using raw GitHub URLs:
   `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MatheusOliveiraSilva/quick-os/main/docs/images/<file>.png`
4. Mermaid blocks in markdown are optional (GitHub web); PNG links are **required** for mobile.
5. Register new diagrams in `docs/DIAGRAMS.md`

Owner preference: Matheus reviews from mobile — diagrams without PNG links are incomplete.
